_json.gridTitle: How to Make Magnesium Oil and Save 90% - Cheeseslave
_json.description: I have had great results with magnesium oil. I spray it on every day. Magnesium is known as the calming mineral, and I don't know about you but most of us could benefit from some stress reduction. Many people find that magnesium oil reduces or eliminates aches and pains, helps them to relax and helps them sleep.  If you would like to save some money, you can make your own magnesium oil using magnesium chloride flakes. Here's how to make your own magnesium oil.
